name: Export Users To PDF
author: Narola Infotech Solutions LLP

sections.description:
This Plugin allows you to export users below informations into PDF file.

  1. User ID
  2. User Name
  3. First Name
  4. Last Name
  5. Email ID
  6. Nick Name
  7. User Role
  8. Registered Date

Kindly let us know your feedback or comments to add more features in this plugin.
sections.installation:
1. Log in to your WordPress admin panel and go to Plugins -> Add New
  2. Type Export Users To PDF in the search box and click on search button.

OR

  1. Download and save the Export Users To PDF plugin to your hard disk.
  2. Login to your WordPress and go to the Add Plugins page.
  3. Click Upload Plugin button to upload the zip.
  4. Click Install Now to install and activate the plugin.
sections.faq:
How to Export users?

  1. Click on Users menu from left side navigation menu
  2. Click on Export Users as PDF button for downloaded all users into PDF file.

short_description: Export Users To PDF Plugin allows you to export users list and their meta data in PDF file.
